POE-Component-Data-SimplePassword

The module is a non-blocking wrapper around L<Data::SimplePassword> (although, the
primary purpose was an event based interface)
which provides interface to generate random passwords.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc POE::Component::Data::SimplePassword

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=POE-Component-Data-SimplePassword

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/POE-Component-Data-SimplePassword

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/POE-Component-Data-SimplePassword

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/POE-Component-Data-SimplePassword


